org.safs.text

Class FileUtilities.FileAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.text.FileUtilities.FileAttribute
  • Enclosing class:
    FileUtilities

    public static class FileUtilities.FileAttribute
extends java.lang.Object
    To model the file attribute.
    APR 06, 2016 (Carl Nagle) Support FileAttribute.ALLFILES Type to specify all non-VOLUMELABEL files at a location.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  FileUtilities.FileAttribute.Type
      An enumeration to specify the file's attributes.
      They can be used one by one, or an bit-combination of them.
